  <name>Toner</name>
  <summary>GTK4 and Libadwaita tone generator</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Toner is a minimalist and intuitive tone generator application built with GTK4 and Libadwaita.
      It can generate various waveforms (sine, square, triangle, sawtooth).
    </p>
    <p>
      Key features include:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Can generate any frequency.</li>
      <li>Four waveforms: Sine, Square, Triangle, and Sawtooth.</li>
      <li>Real-time audio output using PulseAudio.</li>
      <li>A clean, modern, and responsive user interface following GNOME HIG.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
